						               													<description>Snow Day: The Cold War is a medium-light family-friendly tactics game. Our aim is to bring players from a wide range of ages together for a nostalgic and playful snowball fight!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players compete in teams of an equal number of characters(usually 2 per player). On a modular grid, the first team to knock over all of the opponent's snowmen win the game! All players on a team act as one turn, and each character may use 2 actions (Move, Throw, Build forts/snowballs, Break fort, Knockdown Snowman)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Coordinate with your team to move past opponents to their side of the board to knock down the snowmen. Use snow forts to defend your characters and block movement. Slide on ice to increase your mobility. Build and throw snowballs to send players into their houses to warm up before returning to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
